---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="About Me">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-center mb-12">
        A passionate and driven individual with a rich and diverse background. My journey has taken me from the world of culinary arts to the ever-evolving field of technology, where I've found my true calling.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Early Influences & Tech Beginnings</h2>
           <p class="text-lg mb-4">
       I grew up in Lakeland, FL, in a large family with nine siblings. My father, a chemical engineer and software developer, instilled in me an early appreciation for technology. I understood the importance of C and C++ before middle school and quickly became the household's go-to IT support, becoming proficient with DOS by elementary school.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">
       This early exposure sparked a passion for web development, leading me to start a business during the GeoCities and Angelfire era. I designed custom websites, migrated legacy layouts to PHP, and helped clients transition to custom domains. I also ran a business fixing and building computers, further deepening my technical skills.
      </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">A Different Path: The Culinary World</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
           For 17 years, I embarked on a culinary career, working as a cook and chef. This experience, while seemingly different, taught me invaluable lessons in creativity, precision, and working under pressure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Returning to My Roots</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
           In 2021, I decided to return to my original passion and pursue a career in technology. This led me to enroll at Polk State College and, now, the University of South Florida, where I am dedicated to expanding my knowledge and skills in the cybersecurity landscape.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Educational Journey</h2>
          <ul class="timeline">
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">M.S. in Cybersecurity Intelligence & Information Security</h4>
                  <p><small class="text-muted">University of South Florida (Current)</small></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">Bachelor of Applied Science in Supervision & Management</h4>
                  <p><small class="text-muted">Polk State College (2025)</small></p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p>Specialization in Data Analytics.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">Associate in Science in Network Systems Engineering Technology</h4>
                  <p><small class="text-muted">Polk State College (2022)</small></p>
                </div>
                 <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p>Infrastructure Specialization.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
             <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">Collegiate High School</h4>
                  <p><small class="text-muted">Polk Community College (2005-2007)</small></p>
                </div>
                 <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p>IT Program under Cliff Bennett and Brian Hartpence</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
             <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">Harrison School for the Visual and Performing Arts</h4>
                  <p><small class="text-muted">Harrison Crowles (2003-2005)</small></p>
                </div>
                 <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p>Visual Arts Program</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
             <li>
              <div class="timeline-badge"></div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4 class="timeline-title">Rochelle School of the Arts</h4>
                </div>
                 <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p>Orchestra (Cello) and Visual Arts</p>tint
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
.timeline {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 20px 0 20px;
  position: relative;
}

.timeline:before {
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  position: absolute;
  content: " ";
  width: 3px;
  background-color: #eeeeee;
  left: 50%;
  margin-left: -1.5px;
}

.timeline > li {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  position: relative;
}

.timeline > li:before,
.timeline > li:after {
  content: " ";
  display: table;
}

.timeline > li:after {
  clear: both;
}

.timeline > li > .timeline-panel {
  width: 46%;
  float: left;
  border: 1px solid #d4d4d4;
  border-radius: 2px;
  padding: 20px;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.175);
}

.timeline > li > .timeline-badge {
  color: #fff;
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  line-height: 50px;
  font-size: 1.4em;
  text-align: center;
  position: absolute;
  top: 16px;
  left: 50%;
  margin-left: -25px;
  background-color: #999999;
  z-index: 100;
  border-top-right-radius: 50%;
  border-top-left-radius: 50%;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;
}

.timeline > li.timeline-inverted > .timeline-panel {
  float: right;
}

.timeline > li.timeline-inverted > .timeline-panel:before {
  border-left-width: 0;
  border-right-width: 15px;
  left: -15px;
  right: auto;
}

.timeline > li.timeline-inverted > .timeline-panel:after {
  border-left-width: 0;
  border-right-width: 14px;
  left: -14px;
  right: auto;
}

.timeline-title {
  margin-top: 0;
  color: inherit;
}

.timeline-body > p,
.timeline-body > ul {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.timeline-body > p + p {
  margin-top: 5px;
}
</style>